1
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,439
We were

2
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:05,599
planning to wait until you're feeling better

3
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:06,439
before bringing you back,

4
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,680
but there's a new situation now.

5
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:10,719
We thought

6
00:01:10,719 --> 00:01:12,359
that after the spy got Jiaotu No. 1,

7
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,680
they would immediately start production.

8
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:15,040
But it seems

9
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,799
that they haven't made a move yet.

10
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,719
According to our intelligence,

11
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,959
Ke Yu'ang

12
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,519
hasn't made any moves yet.

13
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,640
Captain Feng,

14
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,599
I request to

15
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:28,040
immediately go to Harbor City to investigate.

16
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,000
I know

17
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,719
directly contacting the relics exhibition

18
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:33,079
is easy to arouse suspicion.

19
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,519
I can use Shen's Group

20
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,680
as a business pretext

21
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,840
to discuss business with my old classmate Lin Chuyi.

22
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:39,920
That's the most reasonable excuse.

23
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:41,760
Okay.

24
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,760
Actually, that's what I meant.

25
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,239
When the relics exhibition

26
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:47,159
kept having issues,

27
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,280
she suddenly showed up.

28
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:50,280
I always felt

29
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:51,760
it was too much of a coincidence.

30
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:53,879
Yes.

31
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,680
We're also investigating her.

32
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,079
This is

33
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,200
the address of Lin Chuyi and her team in Harbor City.

34
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:03,439
A foreign-funded hotel

35
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:05,319
invested by the Shan Yuan Foundation.

36
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,079
All the information is inside.

37
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,280
You must be careful.

38
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,120
And

39
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,960
Jiang Xun is staying at this hotel.

40
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,759
We're not sure

41
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:18,199
of the spy's next move yet.

42
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:19,719
But we must

43
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:21,159
[to minimize the risk]

44
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:22,039
[to Jiaotu No.1,]

45
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:23,560
[and]

46
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,439
[gather intelligence]

47
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,280
[to take them all down.]

48
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:29,919
[So the organization has decided]

49
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:31,080
[to send us to Harbor City]

50
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,680
[to prepare for the arrest.]

51
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:34,759
[The situation in Harbor City is complicated.]

52
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:36,400
[Be careful.]

53
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,319
[For security and confidentiality,]

54
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,159
[we'll go separately.]

55
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,520
[During this period,]

56
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,520
[we can only communicate in a single line.]

57
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,319
[I'll support you at any time.]

58
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,560
[I'll finish the mission.]

59
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:24,680
Doesn't your junior sister need your personal care?

60
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:26,759
Secretary Lin, have you found out

61
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:28,080
Shen Shutu's purpose?

62
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,400
Don't think I don't know

63
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,240
what your purpose is.

64
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,240
Do you want to delay the mission because of her?

65
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,520
Is the cryptographic key with her?

66
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:37,759
You'll know soon.

67
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,199
When the relics exhibition

68
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,120
had problems one after another,

69
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:46,479
she suddenly appeared.

70
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:00,279
Who's there?

71
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,079
Who's there?

72
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,360
Where's your manager?

73
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,920
What do you want with him?

74
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,319
Can I help you?

75
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,920
What's going on with your hotel?

76
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,120
There are ghosts at night.

77
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:35,399
The cup broke by itself.

78
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:36,680
The balcony door opened by itself.

79
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:38,279
I'm going to be mentally weak.

80
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,800
How to solve this problem?

81
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:41,279
I'm very sorry, madam.

82
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:43,319
Can we change a room for you?

83
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,360
No.

84
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,240
You must find me a safe place.

85
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,360
Okay.

86
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,360
How about this?

87
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,000
how about we upgrade you for free

88
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,680
to a private apartment under our hotel?

89
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,120
It has 24-hour security,

90
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,800
and it's very safe and private.

91
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,920
You can sign here and check in now.

92
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,040
I have something to do, I'll come find you later.

93
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,680
I'm so sorry.

94
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,120
Who is it?

95
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,560
Who is it?

96
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,480
What do you want?

97
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:27,839
Get away.

98
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,639
I'm sleeping.

99
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,319
Sleeping?

100
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,519
Stop pretending.

101
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:39,839
Stop pretending.

102
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:41,040
What am I pretending?

103
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,839
How do I know what you're doing?

104
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:44,639
I never thought you were such a vulgar person.

105
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,240
Rekindle with your first love, right?

106
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,560
You like this too, right?

107
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,120
So because Lin Chuyi appeared,

108
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,319
because of Lin Chuyi?

109
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,040
We've already broken up.

110
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:54,800
Yeah, I'm that kind of person.

111
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,680
So what?

112
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,439
Do I owe you an explanation

113
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,920
about who I'm with?

114
00:06:58,279 --> 00:07:00,439
The world doesn't revolve around you.

115
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:02,959
Don't you know why she approached you?

116
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,879
Don't you know why she's in Rongzhou?

117
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,879
So you'd rather believe her

118
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,000
than me, huh?

119
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,519
Why should I believe you?

120
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:10,560
I know her family background better than anyone.

121
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,680
I only know you through a blind date.

122
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:13,600
Compared to her,

123
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,680
you're just too easy.

124
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,199
You're a jerk.

125
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:21,240
Yes,

126
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,519
I am a jerk.

127
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,040
Now that you know I'm a jerk,

128
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,959
don't make any excuses

129
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,360
to come back to me.

130
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,319
Understand?

131
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,439
If you do, get out.

132
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:41,519
As you wish.

133
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:43,000
You...

134
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,720
Jiang Xun is being watched.

135
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,399
Someone sneaked into her room at night.

136
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:15,959
Probably looking for something.

137
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:17,600
Who was it?

138
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,879
It was too dark.

139
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:19,800
I couldn't see clearly.

140
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:22,079
But I guessed it was Ke Yu'ang by his figure.

141
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,439
Ke Yu'ang?

142
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,079
Yes.

143
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,759
According to Xu Mo's statement,

144
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:28,279
Xue Li seemed dissatisfied

145
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:30,199
with the seller.

146
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:32,039
So they decided

147
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:34,200
to put the chip inside a jade material with impregnation

148
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,080
for the transaction.

149
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,039
A jade material with impregnation?

150
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:01,519
They didn't get the chip.

151
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,840
There were other people in the room just now.

152
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,519
Someone else is looking for the cryptographic key.

153
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:08,240
Another group of people.

154
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,279
Who?

155
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,639
I don't know.

156
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:13,080
They are good at martial arts.

157
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,559
They can fight with me for a few rounds.

158
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:19,120
Ke Yu'ang,

159
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:22,519
you have two days to deal with this matter.

160
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,720
If you still can't get it,

161
00:09:26,759 --> 00:09:29,440
I'll get it my way.

162
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,639
I warn you,

163
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:33,720
don't hurt her.

164
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:37,879
As colleagues,

165
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:39,320
I'll give you a friendly reminder.

166
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:42,240
Women hate men who hesitate in relationships.

167
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:45,240
You've been dragging your feet for so long.

168
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:46,960
If you don't act now,

169
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:49,840
be careful she'll get back together with Shen Shutu.

170
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,159
Really?

171
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,759
You don't care

172
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:55,360
that Shen Shutu has someone else in his heart?

173
00:09:58,879 --> 00:09:59,879
I do.

174
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,320
I only care about

175
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:05,440
how to use him.

176
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,720
Sometimes,

177
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,120
to achieve your goals,

178
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,279
you have to use some means.

179
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:13,200
Turning a fake play into reality

180
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,679
is not impossible.

181
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,720
Between men and women,

182
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,240
the less you care,

183
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:24,559
the easier it is to get what you want.

184
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,519
Haven't you ever suspected

185
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,080
Shen Shutu is playing you?

186
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:36,320
Someone snatched the key

187
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,679
from me in Jiang Xun's room.

188
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:38,559
I think

189
00:10:38,879 --> 00:10:39,559
it was him.

190
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:41,639
How can you be so sure?

191
00:10:42,159 --> 00:10:43,519
I've been monitoring him all night.

192
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,919
He was sleeping the whole time

193
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,759
until Jiang Xun came to

194
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,639
That's ridiculous.

195
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:52,240
But that stupid woman broke the camera.

196
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:54,320
I have to find another way to keep an eye on him.

197
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,039
Drive.

198
00:11:37,639 --> 00:11:39,720
Article 46 of the Counter-Espionage Law

199
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,960
of the People's Republic of China stipulates

200
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:44,320
that individuals who support or assist in counter-espionage work

201
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,440
and face dangers to their personal safety

202
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,720
or that of their immediate family members

203
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,519
may request protection

204
00:11:50,519 --> 00:11:52,320
from the national security agency.

205
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,840
The state security agency

206
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,639
shall, together with relevant departments,

207
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:57,440
take protective measures in accordance with the law.

208
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,639
The strong motherland

209
00:11:58,639 --> 00:12:01,200
will protect every citizen who fights against spies.

210
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,000
Don't be afraid.

211
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:02,960
The state security agency

212
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,879
is always the most solid backing.
